SELECT e."EventId", e."Title", e."Date", COALESCE(e."Price", 0.0) AS "TicketPrice", COALESCE((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(t."Quantity"), 0)::int
    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t
    WHERE e."EventId" = t."EventId"), 0) AS "TicketsSold", COALESCE((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(t0."TotalPrice"), 0.0)
    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t0
    WHERE e."EventId" = t0."EventId"), 0.0) AS "TotalRevenue"
FROM "Events" AS e
WHERE e."CreatedByUserId" = @__user_Id_0
ORDER BY e."Date" DESC

SELECT e."EventId", e."Title", e."Date", COALESCE(e."Price", 0.0) AS "TicketPrice", COALESCE((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(t."Quantity"), 0)::int
    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t
    WHERE e."EventId" = t."EventId"), 0) AS "TicketsSold", COALESCE((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(t0."TotalPrice"), 0.0)
    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t0
    WHERE e."EventId" = t0."EventId"), 0.0) AS "TotalRevenue"
FROM "Events" AS e
WHERE e."CreatedByUserId" = @__user_Id_0
ORDER BY e."Date" DESC

2025-12-05 00:52:20.512 -05:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__userId_0='?', @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."EventId", e."Title" AS "EventTitle", COALESCE(sum(t."Quantity"), 0)::int AS "TicketsSold", COALESCE(sum(t."TotalPrice"), 0.0) AS "TotalRevenue"
FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t
INNER JOIN "Events" AS e ON t."EventId" = e."EventId"
WHERE e."CreatedByUserId" = @__userId_0
GROUP BY t."EventId", e."Title"

    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t

    SELECT COALESCE(sum(t."Quantity"), 0)::int
    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t
    WHERE e."EventId" = t."EventId"), 0) AS "TicketsSold", COALESCE((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(t0."TotalPrice"), 0.0)
    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t0
    WHERE e."EventId" = t0."EventId"), 0.0) AS "TotalRevenue"

WHERE e."CreatedByUserId" = @__user_Id_0
ORDER BY e."Date" DESC

    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t
    WHERE e."EventId" = t."EventId"), 0) AS "TicketsSold", COALESCE((
    SELECT COALESCE(sum(t0."TotalPrice"), 0.0)
    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t0
    WHERE e."EventId" = t0."EventId"), 0.0) AS "TotalRevenue"
FROM "Events" AS e
WHERE e."CreatedByUserId" = @__user_Id_0
ORDER BY e."Date" DESC

FROM (

    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t

) AS s

SELECT s."Key" AS "Category", COALESCE(sum(s."Quantity"), 0)::int AS "TicketsSold"
FROM (

SELECT s."Key" AS "Category", COALESCE(sum(s."Quantity"), 0)::int AS "TicketsSold"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Quantity", COALESCE(e."Category", 'Uncategorized') AS "Key"
    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t
    INNER JOIN "Events" AS e ON t."EventId" = e."EventId"
) AS s
GROUP BY s."Key"
ORDER BY COALESCE(sum(s."Quantity"), 0)::int DESC
2025-12-05 02:47:52.608 -05:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (9ms) [Parameters=[@__startDate_0='?' (DbType = DateTime)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t0."Year", t0."Month", COALESCE(sum(t0."TotalPrice"), 0.0) AS "Revenue"
FROM (
    SELECT t."TotalPrice", date_part('year', t."PurchasedAtUtc" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC')::int AS "Year", date_part('month', t."PurchasedAtUtc" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC')::int AS "Month"
    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t
    WHERE t."PurchasedAtUtc" >= @__startDate_0
) AS t0
GROUP BY t0."Year", t0."Month"
ORDER BY t0."Year", t0."Month"

SELECT s."Key" AS "Category", COALESCE(sum(s."Quantity"), 0)::int AS "TicketsSold"
FROM (
    SELECT t."Quantity", COALESCE(e."Category", 'Uncategorized') AS "Key"
    FROM "TicketPurchases" AS t
    INNER JOIN "Events" AS e ON t."EventId" = e."EventId"
) AS s
GROUP BY s."Key"
ORDER BY COALESCE(sum(s."Quantity"), 0)::int DESC
